Title: On New Forms of the BRST Transformations
Authors: Victor O. Rivelles
Comments: 4 page, Latex. Title and abstract changed, a misprint corrected and a
  more detailed presentation is provided. Conclusions unchanged
Journal-ref: Class.Quant.Grav. 19 (2002) 2525-2527
\\
  We show how to derive systematically new forms of the BRST transformations
for a generic gauge fixed action. They arise after a symmetry of the gauge
fixed action is found in the sector involving the Lagrange multiplier and its
canonical momentum.
